{"tid":2097690,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"上水鳳溪創新小學一名老師上周六與一位剛確診者短暫共處，請問是做過咩:o)?","createTime":"2020-07-07T03:58:53.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-07T07:03:12.000Z","uid":108201,"like":5,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"9e5af140480f2beb8ac14493ca91bcafdf9253c4","tid":2097690,"uid":108201,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T03:58:53.000Z","msg":"小學生唔知會諗左d咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />？<br />\n<br />\n位於上水的鳳溪創新小學宣布，因一名老師上周六（4日）曾與一位剛確診新冠肺炎患者短暫共處，正待衛生署檢測，學校為謹慎處理，已安排今天（7日）停課一天。至於另一間元朗光明英來學校，校方稱有關教職員已即時在家隔離，校方會安排其主要任教班別到其他課室上課。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oK4M5nv.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoK4M5nv.jpg&h=af0473c1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d18636cac65ee22905132eed113be6912a4f0b0d","tid":2097690,"uid":5178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T04:01:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"480f69d600e821d689b96e7ab57719191e91fb51","tid":2097690,"uid":19552,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T04:02:40.000Z","msg":"做愛"},{"pid":"9e548a9bdb8aee14412a3f7a05b0eac274ffc07e","tid":2097690,"uid":32028,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T04:03:31.000Z","msg":"呢排香港既酒店都好多人Book<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8f2505790d14285e0a53b22d55fbf8ddf37c643","tid":2097690,"uid":108201,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"9e548a9bdb8aee14412a3f7a05b0eac274ffc07e","tid":2097690,"uid":32028,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T04:03:31.000Z","msg":"呢排香港既酒店都好多人Book<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T04:06:57.000Z","msg":"老師：拖手會唔會有bb架？"},{"pid":"4f33bbbd0f1a7528ca66089ed548d7c72f9ce982","tid":2097690,"uid":132810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T04:07:28.000